<taxonomicName authority="Strand, 1907" authorityName="Strand" authorityYear="1907" box="[151,555,680,706]" class="Arachnida" family="Pholcidae" genus="Pholcus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="13" pageNumber="14" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="fragillimus">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,555,680,706]" pageId="13" pageNumber="14">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,390,680,706]" italics="true" pageId="13" pageNumber="14">Pholcus fragillimus</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Strand, E." box="[396,555,680,706]" pageId="13" pageNumber="14" pagination="107 - 215" refId="ref28697" refString="Strand, E. (1907) Sud- und ostasiatische Spinnen. Abhandlungen der naturforschenden Gesellschaft Gorlitz, 25, 107 - 215, pls. 1 - 21." type="journal article" year="1907">Strand, 1907</bibRefCitation>
</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
</heading>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="13.[151,1436,750,919]" pageId="13" pageNumber="14">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,218,750,775]" pageId="13" pageNumber="14">Notes</emphasis>
. For synonymy, redescription, and distribution, see 
<bibRefCitation author="Huber, B. A." box="[808,1017,750,775]" pageId="13" pageNumber="14" pagination="1 - 509" refId="ref27101" refString="Huber, B. A. (2011) Revision and cladistic analysis of Pholcus and closely related taxa (Araneae, Pholcidae). Bonner zoologische Monographien, 58, 1 - 509." type="journal article" year="2011">Huber (2011: 415)</bibRefCitation>
and 
<bibRefCitation author="Huber, B. A. &amp; Colmenares, P. A. &amp; Ramirez, M. J." box="[1074,1301,750,775]" pageId="13" pageNumber="14" pagination="413 - 422" refId="ref27242" refString="Huber, B. A., Colmenares, P. A. &amp; Ramirez, M. J. (2014 b) Fourteen new generic and ten new specific synonymies in Pholcidae (Araneae), and transfer of Mystes Bristowe to Filistatidae. Zootaxa, 3847 (3), 413 - 422. https: // doi. org / 10.11646 / zootaxa. 3847.3.5" type="journal article" year="2014">
Huber 
<emphasis box="[1152,1209,750,775]" italics="true" pageId="13" pageNumber="14">et al.</emphasis>
(2014b
</bibRefCitation>
: 420). Even though the species was originally described from “ 
<collectingCountry box="[719,804,786,811]" name="Sri Lanka" pageId="13" pageNumber="14">Ceylon</collectingCountry>
” (no precise locality data) (
<bibRefCitation author="Strand, E." box="[1115,1256,786,811]" pageId="13" pageNumber="14" pagination="107 - 215" refId="ref28697" refString="Strand, E. (1907) Sud- und ostasiatische Spinnen. Abhandlungen der naturforschenden Gesellschaft Gorlitz, 25, 107 - 215, pls. 1 - 21." type="journal article" year="1907">Strand 1907</bibRefCitation>
), it may well be an introduced species. It ranges from 
<collectingCountry box="[601,715,822,847]" name="Sri Lanka" pageId="13" pageNumber="14">Sri Lanka</collectingCountry>
to 
<collectingCountry box="[761,825,823,846]" name="Japan" pageId="13" pageNumber="14">Japan</collectingCountry>
and is often found in disturbed habitats or even in buildings. In 
<collectingCountry box="[300,409,858,883]" name="Sri Lanka" pageId="13" pageNumber="14">Sri Lanka</collectingCountry>
it has been recorded from Wirawila [
<geoCoordinate box="[826,926,858,883]" direction="north" orientation="latitude" pageId="13" pageNumber="14" precision="55" value="6.288">6.288°N</geoCoordinate>
, 
<geoCoordinate box="[937,1048,859,883]" direction="east" orientation="longitude" pageId="13" pageNumber="14" precision="55" value="81.227">81.227°E</geoCoordinate>
], Colombo [
<geoCoordinate box="[1184,1269,859,883]" direction="north" orientation="latitude" pageId="13" pageNumber="14" precision="555" value="8.92">8.92°N</geoCoordinate>
, 
<geoCoordinate box="[1281,1377,859,883]" direction="east" orientation="longitude" pageId="13" pageNumber="14" precision="555" value="79.92">79.92°E</geoCoordinate>
], and from Peradeniya Botanical Garden [
<geoCoordinate box="[554,654,895,919]" direction="north" orientation="latitude" pageId="13" pageNumber="14" precision="55" value="7.273">7.273°N</geoCoordinate>
, 
<geoCoordinate box="[665,773,894,919]" direction="east" orientation="longitude" pageId="13" pageNumber="14" precision="55" value="80.595">80.595°E</geoCoordinate>
] (
<bibRefCitation author="Huber, B. A." box="[794,933,894,919]" pageId="13" pageNumber="14" pagination="1 - 509" refId="ref27101" refString="Huber, B. A. (2011) Revision and cladistic analysis of Pholcus and closely related taxa (Araneae, Pholcidae). Bonner zoologische Monographien, 58, 1 - 509." type="journal article" year="2011">Huber 2011</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
